description:
The Sun and Moon series follows http://anidb.net/ch6693 [Ash Ketchum] on his new journey in Alola with his companion, http://anidb.net/ch8091 [Pikachu]. He and his mother, http://anidb.net/ch22303 [Deliah], leave for the Alola region on a vacation. However, once seeing the Pokmon School, Ash decides to stay in Alola on a new journey.
From there he adventures across the region with his new http://anidb.net/ch87040 [RotomDex], as well as his new classmates.
